  <brief_title>Consolidation Chemotherapy After Autologous Stem Cell Transplantation for Lymphoid Malignancies</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II Trial of Consolidation Chemothetapy for Patients With Relapse or Refractory Lymphoid Malignancies After Autologous Stem Cell Transplantation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
