    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with relapsed or refracotry NHL or HD: PR or SD after first line salvage
             chemotherapy;

          -  ECOG: 0-2

          -  Tbil &lt; 1.5x ULN and AST/ALT &lt;2.5x ULN

          -  With informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Life expectancy &lt; 3 months

